                  </hi>. I am in the employment of James Rank ins, of 22, Holborn<lb></lb>hill, a hosier—last Thursday afternoon I was behind the counter—I turned round and saw the prisoner in the shop, with another boy—I turned to ring the bell, and saw him move from the counter and snatch at a flannel shirt, which he put under the tail of his coat—I jumped over the counter and seized him, kept him till my master came, and gave him in charge—he threw the shirt to the further end of the shop—they let the other boy go, because they did not know whether he belonged to this one.</p>
